mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI
    participant APIGateway as API Gateway
    participant IdeaBFF as Idea Submission BFF
    participant IdeaOrch as Idea Submission Orchestrator
    participant ServiceAdapter as Service Adapter
    participant IdeaService as Idea Service
    participant IdeaDiscovery as Idea Discovery Service
    participant NotificationAdapter as Notification Adapter
    participant Kafka
    participant Database as PostgreSQL

    User->>UI: 1. Fill idea form (title, description, campaign, confidentiality)
    UI->>APIGateway: 2. POST /bff/v1/ideas/create
    APIGateway->>IdeaBFF: 3. Forward request with JWT token
    IdeaBFF->>IdeaOrch: 4. orchestrateIdeaCreation(ideaData)
    
    Note over IdeaOrch: Orchestration starts
    
    IdeaOrch->>ServiceAdapter: 5. GET /api/v1/services/users/{userId}
    ServiceAdapter-->>IdeaOrch: 6. User profile validated
    
    IdeaOrch->>ServiceAdapter: 7. GET /api/v1/campaigns/{campaignId}
    ServiceAdapter-->>IdeaOrch: 8. Campaign details (active, valid)
    
    IdeaOrch->>ServiceAdapter: 9. POST /api/v1/services/files/upload
    ServiceAdapter-->>IdeaOrch: 10. Display picture URL
    
    IdeaOrch->>IdeaService: 11. POST /api/v1/ideas (status: DRAFT)
    IdeaService->>Database: 12. INSERT INTO ideas
    Database-->>IdeaService: 13. ideaId generated
    IdeaService->>Kafka: 14. Publish event: idea.created
    IdeaService-->>IdeaOrch: 15. { ideaId, status: DRAFT }
    
    IdeaOrch->>IdeaDiscovery: 16. POST /api/v1/discovery/similarity/match
    IdeaDiscovery-->>IdeaOrch: 17. Potential matches: [{ ideaId, matchPercentage, title }]
    
    IdeaOrch-->>IdeaBFF: 18. { ideaId, potentialMatches[] }
    IdeaBFF-->>APIGateway: 19. 201 Created
    APIGateway-->>UI: 20. Response with potential matches
    UI-->>User: 21. Show "Potential Matches" with older ideas
    
    User->>UI: 22. Review matches and confirm submission
    UI->>APIGateway: 23. POST /bff/v1/ideas/submit { ideaId }
    APIGateway->>IdeaBFF: 24. Forward submission request
    IdeaBFF->>IdeaOrch: 25. orchestrateIdeaSubmission(ideaId)
    
    IdeaOrch->>IdeaService: 26. POST /api/v1/ideas/{ideaId}/submit
    IdeaService->>Database: 27. UPDATE ideas SET status='SUBMITTED'
    Database-->>IdeaService: 28. Updated
    IdeaService->>Kafka: 29. Publish event: idea.submitted
    IdeaService-->>IdeaOrch: 30. { ideaId, status: SUBMITTED, generatedIdeaId: "IDEA-2025-001" }
    
    IdeaOrch->>ServiceAdapter: 31. POST /api/v1/services/users/suggest-contributors
    ServiceAdapter-->>IdeaOrch: 32. Suggested contributors
    
    IdeaOrch->>IdeaService: 33. POST /api/v1/ideas/{ideaId}/contributors
    IdeaService-->>IdeaOrch: 34. Contributors added
    
    IdeaOrch->>NotificationAdapter: 35. POST /api/v1/notifications/send
    Note right of NotificationAdapter: Notify contributors about new idea
    NotificationAdapter-->>IdeaOrch: 36. Notifications sent
    
    IdeaOrch-->>IdeaBFF: 37. { ideaId, generatedIdeaId, status: SUBMITTED }
    IdeaBFF-->>APIGateway: 38. 200 OK
    APIGateway-->>UI: 39. Success response
    UI-->>User: 40. "Success! Your Idea ID: IDEA-2025-001"
